{"tid":574860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國西維珍尼亞州 2萬教師罷工爭加薪  公立學校連日停課","createTime":"2018-02-27T18:20:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-28T09:06:28.000Z","uid":41818,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"af49eee8bc6afe3f1bd80f9a768705b7a3b83fb6","tid":574860,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T18:20:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180227/large/1519693227_8a75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180227%2Flarge%2F1519693227_8a75.jpg&h=fd3386e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國西維珍尼亞州約2萬名公立學校教師與1.3萬名員工為爭取加薪與福利，連續3天罷工，走上街頭抗議。<br />\n<br />\n美國全國教育協會指出，西維珍尼亞州教師的收入在全美排名第48位，平均年薪僅4.5萬美元（351萬港元），比全國平均少了近1.3萬美元（101.4萬港元）。教職員與支持者周日晚上聚集在西維珍尼亞州首府查爾斯頓（Charleston）舉行燭光晚會抗議。<br />\n<br />\n這一波走出教室上街抗議的浪潮從上周四開始，州議會通過法案，將在未來4年調薪3%。這是西維珍尼亞州教師4年來第一次加薪，不過教師們認為加薪幅度不夠高，也沒有解決醫保費用越來越高的問題。教師工會已經放話，沒有得到他們的要求罷工就不會結束。<br />\n<br />\n這次教師罷工約影響27.7萬名學生，但家長大多表示支持教師們為自己爭取福利的行動。<br />\n<br />\n不過，事實上在西維珍尼亞州，這樣的罷工行為是違法的。州檢察總長表示他支持教師「提高薪資的呼聲」，但會幫助地方當局執法。西維吉尼亞教育協會回應，他們的律師已經準備好面對任何挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180227/57880093\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180227%2F57880093&d=MP5r6eUwNfSjSFn0NXIBn7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=c4cb471e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180227%2F57880093&h=b6b237cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180227/57880093</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dabb380d542c54675720fe1e1576f00ee2397805","tid":574860,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":32,"score":-32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T18:25:29.000Z","msg":"香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n關香港咩事？"},{"pid":"6f371cc336ee2a7d686025cfcf3d4b0decde9fa6","tid":574860,"uid":121496,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T18:26:30.000Z","msg":"4.5萬美金（315萬港紙？）"},{"pid":"4184632a88e4f281b3e9dd519d5e38b9dda260a8","tid":574860,"uid":160379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T18:27:08.000Z","msg":"平均年薪僅4.5萬美元（351萬港元），比全國平均少了近1.3萬美元（101.4萬港元）"},{"pid":"9bd5e5007a1716b406ac362e22d39936d3b0aff0","tid":574860,"uid":49392,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T18:28:43.000Z","msg":"香港人：要返工，不了<br />\n美國人：要返工?不了"},{"pid":"ec3d327b353beccead717dd84d1bff48cc1d719b","tid":574860,"uid":99568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9bd5e5007a1716b406ac362e22d39936d3b0aff0","tid":574860,"uid":49392,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T18:28:43.000Z","msg":"香港人：要返工，不了<br />\n美國人：要返工?不了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T18:49:21.000Z","msg":"死教畜"},{"pid":"90d3295fb563883e6bb85ee54a080f4c571d6ee9","tid":574860,"uid":92361,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4184632a88e4f281b3e9dd519d5e38b9dda260a8","tid":574860,"uid":160379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T18:27:08.000Z","msg":"平均年薪僅4.5萬美元（351萬港元），比全國平均少了近1.3萬美元（101.4萬港元）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T18:52:44.000Z","msg":"點計"},{"pid":"166cb48f6de359ecca1ff90091fdaab6a4017a9f","tid":574860,"uid":134474,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T18:53:35.000Z","msg":"好似計錯數"},{"pid":"66d73f221697a778e05705af08a3e38f7a5ace97","tid":574860,"uid":33439,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4184632a88e4f281b3e9dd519d5e38b9dda260a8","tid":574860,"uid":160379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T18:27:08.000Z","msg":"平均年薪僅4.5萬美元（351萬港元），比全國平均少了近1.3萬美元（101.4萬港元）"},"citedBy